      "createdAt": "2025-03-06T09:43:43.288Z",
      "author": "kolaai (alfred)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p><strong>New feature: Timed assignment</strong> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/alarm_clock.png?v=13\" title=\":alarm_clock:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":alarm_clock:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Set time in minutes to automations and when a status doesn’t change within the specified time, the item will be re-assigned to the next user in line.</p>\n<p>Meet your SLA’s and ensure that items are addressed in a timely manner.<br />\nRead more about this functionality <a href=\"https://apps.kolaai.com/docs/round-robin-pro/actions/#timed-assign-user-or-teams\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a>.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/b/db0e79b68f6e54d151ffb25a04099cf8c53dd7c8.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/d/b/db0e79b68f6e54d151ffb25a04099cf8c53dd7c8_2_690x300.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"300\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1525×664 51.3 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/b/fbea5dd5490b0210bdb2bc3563776acd3d2c8f77.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/f/b/fbea5dd5490b0210bdb2bc3563776acd3d2c8f77_2_690x355.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"355\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1454×750 45.9 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Try the <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000488/round-robin-pro\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Round Robin Pro</a> app for free!</p>"
